ct those on the grave, O He who cause the ocean to flow, O He who make the iron to be soft to Dawood peace be on him, bless be on Mohammad and on the family of Muhammad and offer me this and this.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ يَا ذَا الْمَجْدِ الشَّامِخِ وَالسُّلْطَانِ الْبَاذِخِ، صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ، وَكُنْ لِوَلِيِّكَ وَابْنِ وَلِيِّكَ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ الْحَسَنِ الْمَهْدِيِّ، فِيْ هٰذِهِ السَّاعَةِ وَلِيًّا وَحَافِظًا، وَقَاۗئِدًا وَنَاصِرًا، وَدَلِيْلًا وَعَوْنًا، وَعَيْنًا وَمُعِيْنًا، حَتّٰى تُسْكِنَهُ اَرْضَكَ طَوْعًا، وَتُمَتِّعَهُ فِيْهَا طَوِيْلًا۔ يَا مُدَبِّرَ الْاُمُوْرِ، يَا بَاعِثَ مَنْ فِي الْقُبُوْرِ، يَا مُجْرِيَ الْبُحُوْرِ، يَا مُلَيِّنَ الْحَدِيْدِ لِدَاوُوْدَ عَلَيْهِ السَّلَامُ، صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ، وَافْعَلْ بِيْ كَذَا وَكَذَا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "Arabi